posts.post_content:
Lot of 11 Beater T202 - SOLD...backs are slightly cleaner and better looking than the fronts.

Includes: 
- Lobert Almost Caught - w/ Cy Young
- Jake Stahl Guarding First - w/ Eddie Cicotte (GD condition - better than others)
- Chase Safe at Third - w/ Home Run Baker (clean end panel on Baker)
- Harry Lord at Third - w/ Joe Tinker
